## 12. Appendices

### Sample Bylaws and Policies
- Example co-op bylaws outlining governance, membership, and decision-making procedures
- Policies on conflict resolution, anti-discrimination, and code of conduct

### Example Pay and Profit-Sharing Calculations
- Sample formulas for base pay, experience/education adjustments, and profit distribution
- Illustrative tables showing how compensation is calculated for different member profiles

### Marketing Materials and Workflow Diagrams
- Sample brochures, pitch decks, and website content
- Visual diagrams of project intake, assignment, and review workflows

### Additional Resources
- Links to co-op development organizations and legal resources
- Templates for client contracts and member agreements
- Training materials and onboarding checklists

These appendices provide practical tools and reference materials to support the effective operation and ongoing development of [Co-op Name].